snippet.title: Coda | Gameplay Trailer #1 | @ACMUCLA  SRS 2023
snippet.description:
PLAY HERE: https://kmacd02.itch.io/coda

Coda is a rhythm-based puzzle platformer designed exclusively for the Playdate console. Made by students at UCLA for Student Run Studios 2023 via ACM studio.

About
Play as a small, music robot wandering through an abandoned underground cave system. The game is a single-player side-scroller game with rhythm-based fights and puzzles. 


Credits
Project Lead: Kenzie MacDougal
Developers: Jeffrey Shen, Alex Hwang, Harry Huang, Michelle Lee
Designers: Preksha Ambrish, Joice He
